"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-06-olympian-issues-statement-removed-inappropriate-behaviour-21368404\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Paraguayanswimmer\\u00a0Luana Alonso\\u00a0has issued a statement after being removed from the Olympic Village for allegedly 'creating an inappropriate atmosphere'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.8124999943797706, \"rank\": 0.23076923076925165, \"text\": \"Luana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 5.854633364959756e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso, 20, competed for Paraguay in the women's 100m butterfly event inParisbut failed to progress from the heats, finishing sixth with a time of 1:03.09.\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9645497300296668, \"rank\": 0.03675317438547448, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after the disappointing outcome, Alonso announced her retirement from the sport to her 600k followers onInstagram.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Swimming: thank you for allowing me to dream, you taught me to fight, to try, perseverance, sacrifice, discipline and many more,' Alonso said.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  'I gave you part of my life and I do not change it for anything in the world because I lived the best experiences of my life, you gave me thousands of joys, friends from other countries that I will always carry them in my heart, unique opportunities.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not goodbye, it's see you soon.'\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso has since been the subject of headlines after theParaguayan Olympic team said she had been removed from the athletes' village just a few days before the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Her presence is creating an inappropriate atmosphere within Team Paraguay,' said Larissa Schaerer, the head of the COP mission.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9645497300296668, \"rank\": 0.03675317438547448, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larissa Schaerer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\"}, {\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\", \"score\": 0.9995304618218811, \"rank\": 0.0002644663984403718, \"text\": \"COP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We thank her for proceeding as instructed, as it was of her own free will that she did not spend the night in the athletes' village.'\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to claims she created an 'inappropriate atmosphere', Alonso said: 'I just wanted to clarify that I was never kicked out or expelled from anywhere, please stop spreading false information.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not want to make any statement but I am not going to let lies affect me either.'\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso, who was born in Asuncion, made her Olympic debut at the last Games but also failed to challenge for a medal in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asuncion_Island\", \"score\": 0.9901457869990256, \"rank\": 0.00994492078330046, \"text\": \"Asuncion\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asuncion_Island\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asuncion_Island\"}, {\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9994704402180844, \"rank\": 0.000529839154908474, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her latest Olympic setback, Alonso said: 'It did not happen the way I wanted it to.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I sincerely apologise to Paraguay, but I did what I could, despite several things that happened to me before.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1926, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9645497300296668, \"rank\": 0.03675317438547448, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, I am happy and also to retire here with a full stadium and finally have the Olympic Games.'\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:'I will not get them!'\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Why Team GB star Keely Hodgkinson will not add Olympic rings to her tattoo collection  ArrowMORE:Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix says she 'did not want to be alive three years ago' after Olympic disappointment  ArrowMORE:Why are some scores crossed out in diving at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2284, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get your favourite puzzles when they are ready to play on the website sent directly to you every day and track your daily streak!\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your